https://app.opus.com/app/workflow/share/3cc4e4db-0ead-4c9a-be30-a1f7d8298446

This workflow rapidly evaluates a product's standing by aggregating and analyzing genuine user feedback, extracting pros and cons, 
and cross-validating these insights against a broad set of user signals to classify the product as legitimately good, overhyped, mediocre, or fake.
Industry: Retail & E-commerce - Retail Analytics

Inputs & Outputs


Input


Unique product identifier (e.g., SKU, ASIN, or product name)

Collection of user feedback entries related to the product

Output
Product quality label: one of 'legitimately_good', 'overhyped', 'mediocre', or 'fake'

Summary of validated pros and cons with supporting user signal statistics
